data.description: On a charming pine tree-lined street, this 3 bed, 2 bath home is a must-see! Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the fresh and inviting atmosphere. The carpet, blinds, and kitchen appliances suite were all replaced in 2020. The neutral tones and abundant natural light create an airy and welcoming ambiance. Popcorn ceilings are a thing of the past here, making maintenance a breeze. AC unit was replaced in May 2023, ensuring year-round comfort. Stepping outside, you'll find a fenced backyard so if you have children or pets, this space offers a safe and enjoyable environment. For those who love to tinker or have a collection of toys, the oversized 2+ car garage accessible from the alley provides ample space for storage, a workshop, or simply parking your vehicles with ease.
